Configuration files and some handy scripts

.bashrc
.inputrc
.tmux.conf
.vimrc
.Xdefaults
.xinitrc
.zshrc
bin/browser.sh - dmenu to launch browser sessions
bin/comix.sh - dmenu to launch comix
bin/gmail.sh - periodically download gmail feed to a file
bin/lyrics.sh - dump lyrics according to search string
bin/mntnir.sh - CLI volume mounter
bin/mpdplay.sh - create and play MPD playlists according to a string or dmenu
bin/pager.sh - more for short files, less for long ones
bin/red.sh - create and execute redshift commands
bin/remote.sh - control mplayer2 or MPD remotely, for the media keys
bin/status.sh - status line for tmux
bin/vidplay.sh - dmenu to launch mplayer from a background tmux session
bin/vol.sh - set the alsa master volume and refreshe the status bar
bin/webvidplay.sh - use dl-youtube to wget and play a video from the Web
bin/w.sh - simple web searches for the terminal (w3m.vim or plain dump)
bin/xchroot.sh - chroot with x auth, proc, sys, dev and dev/pts
